  "description": "The attractor disturbed. chaosIndex 0.5, leash 0.55 — the uncanny middle from OURO-II, neither noise nor pitch, suspended in the zone where the system is recognizably structured but refusing resolution. Mod wheel injects external force from 0 to 0.22, below the 0.3 ceiling: at low throw the orbit holds shape, at high throw it begins to stagger, each note-on arriving at a slightly different phase. Aftertouch controls damping — press into a held note and the system loosens its grip, harmonics spreading. The performer is not playing notes; they are disturbing an autonomous process.",
